column4: NSLOCTEXT("[1D289A7F4FF6C5743158D2A46C1EAA8C]", "745531C046B22AFDA6232D965012C91F", "Oh no, he\'s coming right for us!")
NSLOCTEXT("[1D289A7F4FF6C5743158D2A46C1EAA8C]", "EC1FD42A41A9862ECE5F469940057EDA", "I finally met you! I\'m Greymon. Now let\'s settle things!")
NSLOCTEXT("[1D289A7F4FF6C5743158D2A46C1EAA8C]", "C16E0E5A495C9A504536D1AC21567C70", "I got here by following the rumors about you. I want to fight you!")
NSLOCTEXT("[1D289A7F4FF6C5743158D2A46C1EAA8C]", "B9351C484ED50704565C32A13E7C680B", "If I win, I want this street sign!")
NSLOCTEXT("[1D289A7F4FF6C5743158D2A46C1EAA8C]", "D832152A490F903F2506FC913CFD3677", "Hey, you guys are good! But to finish your goal, you\'re still amateurs.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1D289A7F4FF6C5743158D2A46C1EAA8C]", "413B8E1C429E9B88E41D78AA5DEBA0E7", "I\'ll stay and train you. You\'ll get much better!")
